			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": "LSString",
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Murder Tribunal (goto -1284 1 504) (near S_LOW_MurderTribunal_Sarevok_ae9f784a-ea64-4297-95a7-8377e85231b6)\r\n- If you want to do the trial, use \"MT_GetDolorItems\" to get one of the victim's hands.\r\n- Get spotted by the members of the court (Sarevok or his three servants).\r\n- This can also be triggered by entering a checkpoint trigger."
				},
